{"tid":1569793,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲無恥 點解國際傳媒唔覺得一回事","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T18:27:06.000Z","uid":268516,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce4cabb43bde505b21a37c87e4a5538c0d4cb95","tid":1569793,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:55:00.000Z","msg":"我有啲野諗唔明<br />\n我地做每一樣野，總有人走出黎，話咁樣唔好睇<br />\n俾國際傳媒影到，或者驚到時佢地喺外國唔知講咩<br />\n<br />\n黑警胡作非為都算國際媒體有講過<br />\n之但係<br />\n藍絲呢？藍絲班人咁耐以黎做嘅野，<br />\n國際輿論係點？都係幾句報導完就算？<br />\n<br />\n咁點解我地掟吓野 變吓魔法<br />\n次次都有人話國際輿論會轉向？<br />\n<br />\n點解永遠係我地受欺壓嗰陣<br />\n欺壓嗰一方好似無乜後果<br />\n但係我地只要唔係聖人<br />\n就會俾人針對住？<br />\n<br />\n試吓如果係我地拎𠝹刀亂咁舞？<br />\n試吓如果係我地斬人？<br />\n肯定唔會好似班藍絲咁做完無後果  國際社會無視<br />\n<br />\n點解個世界咁痴線嘅?"},{"pid":"2ef1402fd4eb3e99a03a5dca5a20d98fab5f352a","tid":1569793,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=ffcd01a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=ca72296e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"33530995ffa4b46d86d63512987f73dc7be34253","tid":1569793,"uid":322337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"因為手足門是站在道德高地去抗爭，而藍絲不是，所以本來就是不對等的。"},{"pid":"9c4e98e9ff31aa672027deb3f586fd128daf10c1","tid":1569793,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:10:05.000Z","msg":"美國騷亂搶掠你會擺幾多篇幅報道<br />\n黃背心幾慘烈你又花幾多時間去關注<br />\n唔係自己地方咁梗係唔多關